OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has
OL,7,Funcovered numerous allegations of
OL,8,Finappropriate and intimidating
OL,9,Fbehaviour by celebrity chef Gino
OL,10,FD'Acampo.
OL,12,FDozens of people have detailed
OL,13,Fexperiences described variously as
OL,14,F"unacceptable," "distressing" and
OL,15,F"horrendous" while working with him
OL,16,Fover a period spanning more than 12
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
