OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,FAnd ITV News has seen evidence which
OL,7,Fshows at least one production company
OL,8,Fwas aware of multiple complaints made
OL,9,Fby members of their crew about Gino
OL,10,FD'Acampo ` but continued to work with
OL,11,Fhim on further TV programmes.
OL,13,FResponding to the claims, D'Acampo
OL,14,Ftold ITV News he "firmly denied" the
OL,15,Fallegations, adding they were "deeply
OL,16,Fupsetting".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
