OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,FThe production companies, which made
OL,7,Fthe TV programmes detailed in the
OL,8,Fallegations, and the channel which
OL,9,Fbroadcast the shows, provided the
OL,10,Ffollowing statements:
OL,12,F"ITV is completely committed to
OL,13,Fcreating an environment where everyone
OL,14,Fis treated with respect and feels able
OL,15,Fto give of their best.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
