OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,F"Our promise to those we work with is
OL,7,Fthat where a complaint is made, or
OL,8,Fserious concern raised, we will always
OL,9,Finvestigate and if we find that
OL,10,Fsomething inappropriate has happened,
OL,11,Fwe will take action. The same
OL,12,Fstandards are expected of all
OL,13,Fproduction companies who make
OL,14,Fprogrammes on ITV's behalf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
