OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,F"It is production companies who have
OL,7,Fthe primary responsibility for the
OL,8,Fduty of care of everyone they work
OL,9,Fwith, both on and off screen, when
OL,10,Fmaking shows. We make clear our
OL,11,Fexpectations of producers and have
OL,12,Frobust and comprehensive policies
OL,13,Fwhich we implement contractually.
OL,15,F"We have strengthened these policies
OL,16,Fin the last 5 years and have set up a
OL,17,Fdedicated Complaints Handling Unit in
OL,18,F2024 to manage any complaints we
OL,19,Freceive about on screen presenters and
OL,20,Fensure ITV has a centralised view
OL,21,Facross different productions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
