OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,F"The standards of behaviour that ITV
OL,7,Fexpects are very clear. Everyone
OL,8,Fworking with ITV is subject to ITV's
OL,9,FCode of Ethics and Conduct. At ITV we
OL,10,Ftreat everyone with courtesy,
OL,11,Ffairness, dignity and respect and do
OL,12,Fnot tolerate abusive behaviour of any
OL,13,Fform in the workplace.
OL,15,F"We have also reiterated our
OL,16,Fexpectations of our on screen
OL,17,Fpresenters' behaviour through our
OL,18,FConduct and Standards Guidelines for
OL,19,FOn Screen Personalities issued in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
