OL,3,CGino D'Acampo: Production companies'
OL,4,Cresponses in full
OL,6,F"Studio Ramsay have not worked on a
OL,7,Fseries with Gino D'Acampo since 2022.
OL,9,F"Whilst we do not disclose or discuss
OL,10,Fpersonnel matters publicly, Studio
OL,11,FRamsay is committed, in conjunction
OL,12,Fwith our broadcast partners, to a safe
OL,13,Fand professional work environment. We
OL,14,Ftake all allegations of inappropriate
OL,15,Fbehaviour and workplace misconduct
OL,16,Fseriously, promptly investigate, and
OL,17,Ftake appropriate remedial action when
OL,18,Fwarranted."
OL,20,FMultiStory Media, which produced
OL,21,F'Gino's Italian Express'
